-- U.S. court orders Allergan to produce board documents
-- By Shailesh Kuber
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 05:13PM EDT
-- None



Sept 22 (Reuters) - A U.S. court ordered drugmaker Allergan Inc <AGN.N> to produce board documents related to its strategy to counter the hostile bid by William Ackman's Pershing Square Capital Management and Canada's Valeant Pharmaceuticals International <VRX.TO> <VRX.N>.

